cufy.io.loadable

Interface FormatLoadable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Loadable

    public interface FormatLoadable
extends Loadable
    An object that can be loaded from a container. And that container provides an unformatted data that requires that loadable to format it.
    Since:
    13-Feb-2020
    Version:
